name: Virgin Trains East Coast First Class - London to Newcastle
description:
Snapchat: pauls_trips
Twitter: @pauls_trips

A fine journey with Virgin Trains between London King's Cross and Newcastle Central stations. The trip, taking just over three hours, is in First Class. Enjoy the lounge, ambience and a delicious evening meal service on board - all included in the price. 

Enjoy the video, and don't forget to subscribe!
